Field Detail

TABLE_KEYWORDS

public static java.lang.String[] TABLE_KEYWORDS
TABLE_KEYWORDS: lists the possible beginning keywords of table captions, which are extracted by PDF text extractors. These keywords are very helpful for table caption detection and the table boundary detection.

FIGURE_KEYWORDS

public static java.lang.String[] FIGURE_KEYWORDS
FIGURE_KEYWORDS: lists the possible beginning words of figure captions, which are extracted by PDF text extractors.

DEBUG_MODE

public static boolean DEBUG_MODE
DEBUG_MODE: this parameter is used for debugging purpose. The default value is "false". If we want to see the debug results, it should be set as "true". The middle-stage results will be printed in the screen and saved locally. Once it is set as "true", the system will call "Debug.java".

SMALL_TEST

public static boolean SMALL_TEST
SMALL_TEST: this parameter is used for small-scale testing.
